      "score": 14,
      "comments": 6,
      "author": "confusedalex",
      "published": "2026-07-03T23:23:43Z",
      "bullets": [
        "Leverage GitOps pipelines using ArgoCD or Flux on K3s to automate deployments and eliminate manual drift correction.",
        "Use Renovate bot and container image updaters like Keel to automatically apply dependency and package updates without manual intervention.",
        "Define homelab infrastructure using Terraform and Ansible to ensure reproducible, zero-maintenance rebuilds when hardware or OS failures occur."
      ]
    },
